Package com.github._1c_syntax.bsl.parser

Interface BSLMethodDescriptionParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BSLMethodDescriptionParserBaseListener
    public interface BSLMethodDescriptionParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by BSLMethodDescriptionParser.
